ContractMetadata.name: get
ContractMetadata.summary: Get the metadata associated with this contract.

ContractMetadata.name: set
ContractMetadata.summary: Set the metadata associated with this contract.

examples.python:
from thirdweb.types import ContractMetadataSchema

metadata = ContractMetadataSchema.from_json({
    "name": "My Contract",
    "description": "This is my contract!",
    "image": open("path/to/file.jpg", "rb")
})

receipt = contract.metadata.set(metadata)

PlatformFee.name: get
PlatformFee.summary: Get the platform fee of this contract.

PlatformFee.name: set
PlatformFee.summary: Set the platform fee of this contract.

examples.python:
from thirdweb.types import ContractPlatformFeeSchema

platform_fee_info = ContractPlatformFeeSchema(
    platform_fee_basis_points=100 # 1%
    platform_fee_receipient="{{wallet_address}}"
)

receipt = contract.platform_fee.set(platform_fee_info)

Permissions.name: get
Permissions.summary: Get all members of a role on this contract.

examples.python:
from thirdweb.constants.role import Role

# Select any role to filter by
role = Role.ADMIN

role_members = contract.roles.get(role)
print(role_members)

Permissions.name: grant
Permissions.summary: Grant a role to an address.

examples.python:
from thirdweb.constants.role import Role

address = "{{wallet_address}}" # Address to grant a role
role = Role.ADMIN # Select a role to grant

receipt = contract.roles.grant(role, address)

    NFTMetadataInput.from_json({

        "description": "This is a cool NFT",

    100
)

receipt = tx.receipt

nft = tx.data()
